      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">8</infon>
        <offset>891</offset>
        <text>T. weissflogii did not aggregate in axenic culture, and striking differences in aggregation dynamics and TEP abundance were observed when diatom cultures were inoculated with either diatom-attaching or free-living bacteria.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1115</offset>
        <text>The data indicated that free-living bacteria might not influence aggregation whereas bacteria attaching to diatom cells may increase aggregate formation.
</text>
